        "en.hubeali": [
          "A number of our companions, from Sahl Bin Ziyad, from Ali Bin Asbaat, from Al hassan Bin Kuleyb, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘The laughter of the <span class=\"iTxt\">Momin</span> is a smile’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "5. A number of our people have narrated from Sahl ibn Ziyad from Ali ibn Asbat from al-Hassan ibn Kulayb from abu ‘Abd Allah (a.s.) who has said the following: “The laughing of a believing person is smiling.” "
        ]
